"Number 2100 is a blend of the attributes and energies of number 2 and number 1, and the influences of number 0 appearing twice, amplifying the vibrations of the numbers it appears with. \tNumber 2\tbrings balance, healing, harmony, devotion and grace, duality, diplomacy and adaptability, partnership and relationships, sensitivity and selflessness, decisiveness, co-operation and consideration. Number 2 also resonates with serving your\tlife purpose\tand\tsoul mission\t. \tNumber 1\tresonates with creativity and creation, new beginnings and taking different directions, motivation and progress, self-reliance, striving forward and pursuing goals, achievement and inspiration, and also relates to\tcreating our own realities\twith our thoughts, beliefs and actions. \tNumber 0\tstands for potential and/or choice,\tdeveloping one’s spiritual aspects\t, listening to your intuition and higher-self, eternity and infinity, oneness and wholeness, continuing cycles and flow, and the beginning point. Number 0 powerfully amplifies the energies of the numbers it appears with.\tAngel Number 2100 suggests that there may be some new opportunities or directions for you to take that will lead you towards new and exciting situations and circumstances. Be aware of your thoughts as they are\tmanifesting\tyour ideas and beliefs into reality, so maintain a\tpositive attitude\tregarding current changes and/or circumstances as this will help to\tmanifest\tyour desired results and outcomes. Trust that your\tangels\tare by your side as you look to new and/or different directions and are guiding your every step. Remain calm, balanced and happy and you will find that all will work out for your highest good.\tAngel Number 2100 indicates that things will be going in your desired direction and wonderful opportunities will present themselves when the timing is right. Your\tangels\tand\tspirit guides\tencourage you to maintain faith and trust, knowing that you are fully supported in every way. Your\tangels\tare always a step ahead of you so listen to their wisdom to gain confidence in your choices and actions.\tAngel Number 2100 may also suggest that it is time to look to new and/or different ways to enhance your home, garden and surrounds. Usher some fresh, positive energies into your home and family environment and make time for family and social gatherings and celebrations.\t\tNumber 2100 relates to\tnumber 3\t(2+1+0+0=3) and\tAngel Number 3\t.\t*\tJoanne Walmsley\tSacred Scribes\tNUMEROLOGY\t- The Vibration and Energy of Numbers"
